description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 64, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 64, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Stringalong for East, 8 for South, and Stringalong for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30641-17871-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [64 Votes, Common]
